			<p><strong><a href="#comment-228314">Wristband - display</a></strong></p>
	
			<p class="commentbody">I just read your paragraph, and I am surprised people now thinking about put a video display in their wrist. Beside the electronic part of the display, in order for the product of be successful, the way to hold you display on the wrist comfortably is also an challenging aspect. The simple Velcro stripe seem to me won't provide good support on your wrist when wearing the display in a war time, for big movement and long period of time. I think in the way to carry the display need to be improved.<br />I would like to see this "video display on your wrist" coming out with a great success. This is a great idea.</p>
